2.2 Simplified keyword configuration
====================================

The new keyword configuration system is clearer and more maintainable:

   • *One mapping instead of many variables* - Replace individual
     keyword variables (‘org-gtd-next’, ‘org-gtd-todo’, etc.)  with a
     single ‘org-gtd-keyword-mapping’ structure
   • *Global TODO keywords* - No more file-level ‘#+TODO:’ lines that
     can conflict.  Use Emacs' global ‘org-todo-keywords’ configuration
     instead
   • *Automatic validation* - Org GTD validates your keyword
     configuration and provides helpful error messages if something is
     wrong
   • *Better Emacs 29+ support* - Use ‘setopt’ for automatic validation
     when setting variables

   See *note Configuration options: Tell me all the levers I can pull.
for details.


