3.3.1 Basic setup
-----------------

You need to configure three things for org-gtd to work:

  1. *TODO keywords*: Configure ‘org-todo-keywords’ with your GTD
     workflow states
  2. *Keyword mapping*: Map GTD semantic states to your keywords with
     ‘org-gtd-keyword-mapping’
  3. *org-edna*: Enable org-edna with inheritance for project
     dependencies to work

   See the configuration sections below for details.

   *Optional*: Enable ‘org-gtd-mode’ if you want to see your inbox count
in the mode-line (e.g., ‘GTD[5]’).


