     *Example*:
          '((name . "Calendar Items")
            (type . calendar))

   • ‘(type . project)’

     *Matches*: Project headings (‘ORG_GTD="Projects"’)

     *Use case*: List all projects

     *Example*:
          '((name . "All Projects")
            (type . project))

   • ‘(type . active-project)’

     *Matches*: Projects with at least one active (non-done) task

