     *Use case*: Review tickler items

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Tickler Items")
            (type . tickler))

   • ‘(type . someday)’

     *Matches*: Items with ‘ORG_GTD="Someday"’ (someday/maybe with no
     specific timeframe)

     *Use case*: Review someday/maybe list

     *Example*:
          '((name . "Someday/Maybe")
            (type . someday))

   • ‘(type . habit)’

     *Matches*: Items with ‘ORG_GTD="Habits"’

     *Use case*: See all habits

     *Example*:
          '((name . "All Habits")
            (type . habit))

   • ‘(type . next-action)’

     *Matches*: Single action items (‘ORG_GTD="Actions"’) with TODO
