7.5 Tasks still showing after tickler'ing project
=================================================

*Symptom*: Tickler'd a project but some tasks still appear in engage
view.

   *Diagnosis*:
   • Multi-project tasks (tasks shared between projects) are not
     tickler'd
   • If task belongs to Project A and Project B, and you only tickler
     Project A, the task stays visible

   *Solution*:
   • Check task's ORG_GTD_PROJECT_IDS property to see which projects it
     belongs to
   • Either tickler all projects the task belongs to, or remove it from
     one project first
   • During tickler, watch for "Skipping multi-project task" messages

   *Recommended workflow*:
  1. Before tickler'ing: review the project for multi-project tasks
  2. Decide: should this task stay active (part of other project) or be
     tickler'd too?
  3. If tickler'ing: tickler all projects it belongs to
  4. If staying active: accept that it will remain visible


